    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that the seven assessed factors demonstrate a consistent pattern of partial compliance, the Monte Carlo UQ ensemble provides 95th-percentile NIH predictions below the clinical threshold, and the ValidationResult provenance chains are fully traceable to experimental evidence. Six epistemic gaps are acknowledged and documented. The primary credibility claim is considered adequately supported by the surrounding validation evidence. Submission proceeds to regulatory review with open gap register.",
